[BELL RINGING SOMBERLY]

91
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:42,395
 Who died?

92
00:07:42,395 --> 00:07:44,230
 [BULGARIAN]

93
00:07:44,230 --> 00:07:46,715
 [BULGARIAN]

94
00:07:46,715 --> 00:07:48,470
 The owner.

95
00:07:48,470 --> 00:07:50,362
Your friend.

96
00:07:50,362 --> 00:07:51,570
 You're joking, right?

