248
00:17:33,028 --> 00:17:38,570
Every half an hour, someone's pointin' at me.

249
00:17:38,570 --> 00:17:39,470
 Hello there.

250
00:17:39,470 --> 00:17:43,590
(SINGING) And once in while, I feel the shadow of the guilt

251
00:17:43,590 --> 00:17:45,084
I'm passing by.

252
